<ab facs="#facs_268_r3l11"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wellet daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt . vnd auch Jr </ab>
