<ab facs="#facs_268_r3l13"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> darauſʒ durch eẅr <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rſchaft</expan> vnd gepıete <expan>ſıch<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
